cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep convolutional neural networks applied to medical image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the challenges of applying 2D CNN to 3D anisotropic volumes, which is a problem in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of focal loss for more effective learning is a technique used in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
